                        Laravel Admin Portal Project Documentation 


Submitted by: Anujith Suresh 
Date: 21/05/2025 
Project Name: Admin Portal 
Framework Used: Laravel 
Laravel Framework Version: 12.14.1 
PHP Version: 8.2.0 
Database: MySQL 
Database Name: admin-portal 
Setup Instructions:  
1. git clone https://github.com/anujithsuresh/admin-portal.git  
2. Run composer install  
3. Run npm install  
4. Run npm run dev  
5. cp .env.example .env  
6. Set .env with DB credentials  
7. Run php artisan key:generate  
8. Run php artisan migrate  
9. Start server: php artisan serve 
Change URL for API 
C:\Users\ws\admin-portal\resources\views\api\index.blade.php 
fetch(`http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/entity?id=${customerId}`) (Change this line with your url for API)  